Mode Function:

We are making Mode Function to Impute Mode on Categorical Columns where values are Nulls.

getmode <- function(v) {
  uniqv <- unique(v)
  uniqv[which.max(tabulate(match(v, uniqv)))]
}

Linear Regression Modelling :
